main event: On 17 April 1966, two witnesses observed a yellow-white, elliosesent object that appeared similar to an electric arc weld as it took off.
interesting points: The object was seen moving at approximately 15 MPH,The observation lasted for about 5 minutes,The sighting took place in Philomath, Oregon,The observers reported the conditions as clear with some fog patches,The conclusion of the report was that the sighting was an automobile or Venus.
